1290,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:28:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好撚重要！唔該幫手推啊！！推得好辛苦！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【唔想輸嘅入嚟幫手置頂】如何避免被人鳩帶風向+攻破白色恐怖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1361315\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1361315</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8b80d74a057c29808b2997b758599934253042c9","tid":1361493,"uid":131696,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:29:02.000Z","msg":"暫緩完未重啟囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0430d9c31ddedf4c97d4b7eba045b85b801728ed","tid":1361493,"uid":136662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:29:18.000Z","msg":"散貨場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da84caad98b1df54920caffa4132fa55c827fa80","tid":1361493,"uid":80666,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:29:58.000Z","msg":"全港都知電腦節貴過平時,最好永遠都唔好搞"},{"pid":"31ae4386e6309ccad2dcd3d3c3c01a92486e77aa","tid":1361493,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":36,"score":-36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:32:54.000Z","msg":"而家有幾多人會逐樣砌parts <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n高登轉晒nb 場<br />\n黃金直情係平價parts(賣磁能線)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec6bcf4b041cfc213cefec5796969b14c68e368e","tid":1361493,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:36:30.000Z","msg":"明智"},{"pid":"96ee8ef198c21ff0e3acc8c0c182d4c1e6d8a7e6","tid":1361493,"uid":287844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:36:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">時間無多，<br />\n幫手推翻<strong>機場集會行動post</strong>上熱門</span></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">機場就係重要嘅命脈，<br />\n發揮和理非最大影響力，<br />\n到時就有bargaining power!!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n遍地開花，可以向外國旅客宣揚香港嘅運動。派多國語言嘅宣傳, 播大電視。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">星星之火可燎原<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n但如果引發到罷工<br />\n少人上貨同行李<br />\n空運減慢&amp;nbsp;<br />\n減怛機倉清理&amp;nbsp;<br />\n冇人維修飛機&amp;nbsp;<br />\n唔夠人手指揮航空交通，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">泊位費成本每秒鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n所帶來既嘅<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">係世界性影響<br />\n</span></span><br />\n到時各國都要理<br />\n係衝擊所達唔到<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">對準弱點 發揮和理非最強影響力</span></span><br />\n￼￼￼￼￼<br />\n<br />\n一齊入機場嘆冷氣[/orange][/size=5]<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Link:&amp;nbsp;</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1354831\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1354831</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"bf30e3b4a8a094f51141a4ea5098475bd51e4334","tid":1361493,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:39:09.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"d8791be8136853059b703a9e57a13fcd47f25512","tid":1361493,"uid":190281,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:50:08.000Z","msg":"其實係驚政府又封鳩佢地 要蝕租<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83f3edf3b75a3e422112a166291622142b7de5a6","tid":1361493,"uid":43517,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"d8791be8136853059b703a9e57a13fcd47f25512","tid":1361493,"uid":190281,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"re